countyourscores (1.0.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Number sets can now be edited and deleted
  * Remembers the last used number set
  * Optional black theme
  * Different shade of red ("firebrick") as selected player color on the white theme
  * Undo, Next game and Clear all are now text buttons instead of icon buttons
  * Undo button is disabled when there is nothing to undo
  * Asks confirmation before clearing all scores
  * Cannot create a sets with an empty name
  * Added view no longer truncates numbers with more than three digits
  * Added a link to the web page with instructions on the about page
  * Link to the source code on the about page points directly to the sources of the version for Fremantle

 -- Heli Hyvättinen <heli.hyvattinen@netti.fi>  Wed, 03 Jul 2013 23:34:48 +0300

